products.title: Infusion Cream Pleated Skylight Blind
products.description: Their range of infusion pleated blinds is an excellent alternative to a venetian or roller blind. The infusion cream pleated skylight blind will transform the look of your home. Ideal for sloping windows, this beautiful blind is elegant and stylish. Product id: db-pls0002 fabric colour: cream headrail: white rails and hardware with pull down tab and visible guide wires to support the blind fabric.
